The,APPELLO,API,was,developed,to,connect,to,sets,of,EpiDoc,encoded,documents,and,to,extract,information,from,them,EpiDoc,is,a,set,of,guidelines,for,the,structured,markup,of,epigraphic,documents,in,TEI,XML,This,API,is,provided,by,the,Centre,for,the,Study,of,Ancient,Documents,and,The,British,Museum,It,can,be,accessed,using,REST,calls,in,XML,format